'''飓风弗兰克'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Frank}}）是[[2010年太平洋飓风季|2010年太平洋飓风季]]的最后一场飓风，该季一共只形成三场飓风，是有纪录以来最少的一年<ref>{{cite report | author = Hurricane Specialist Unit | date = 2010-12-01 | title = Monthly Tropical Weather Summary | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133115/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/tws/MIATWSEP_nov.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/tws/MIATWSEP_nov.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。风暴源自[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]的雷暴区，于8月21日在墨西哥以南近海成为第九{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压。气旋向西北方向移动，成为热带低气压仅12小时后就升级成热带风暴并获名“弗兰克”。系统达到的第一波强度高峰属中等强度热带风暴，然后在8月23日晚因[[风切变|风切变]]增多而减弱。气旋之后再度增强，于8月25日达到飓风标准。弗兰克的最高强度接近一级飓风标准上限，之后迅速减弱，于8月28日消散。虽然这场风暴自始至终没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但依然对[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西部构成影响，受灾人数超过80万，共有六人丧生。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Frank 2010 track.png}}
弗兰克的源头可以追溯到离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸进入大西洋的[[东风波|东风波]]。[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]附近形成大规模雷暴区，东风波经过加勒比海并发展出中层环流，大气对流也随之波动。天气系统穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]，降水和雷暴活动增多<ref name="FrankTCR">{{cite report | author = Lixion A. Avila | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2010-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | title = Hurricane Frank Tropical Cyclone Report | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071534/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP092010_Frank.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP092010_Frank.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>，于8月19日在墨西哥以南约185公里海域形成大范围[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref name="TWO1">{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203244/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201008201916/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201008201916 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2010-08-20 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201008201916/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201008201916 | deadurl = no | author = Micheal Brennan | publisher = National Hurricane Center }}</ref>。系统所在海域环境有利，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此预计系统会逐渐发展<ref name="TWO2">{{cite report | last = Micheal Brennan | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201008202033/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201008202033 | date = 2010-08-19 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193416/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201008202033/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201008202033 }}</ref>。8月21日，[[对流|对流]]的组织已有改善<ref name="TWO3">{{cite report | last = Micheal Brennan | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2010-08-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151030133203/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201008211148/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201008211148 | archivedate = 2015-10-30 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201008211148/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201008211148 }}</ref>，还发展出弧形[[雨带|雨带]]。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月21日下午18点，气象机构开始针对位于[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]][[萨利纳克鲁斯|萨利纳克鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Salina Cruz}}）东南方向约330公里洋面的第九{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压发布公告<ref name="FrankTCR" />。

成为[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]后，风暴所在海域环境有利于热带天气系统发展，不但[[海面温度|水温]]接近30[[摄氏度|°C]]，而且[[风切变|风切变]]也较弱。美国国家飓风中心因此预测气旋强度可以达到飓风下限<ref name="Disc 1">{{cite report | title = Tropical Depression Nine-E Discussion 1 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171538/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.001.shtml | date = 2010-09-21 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | author = Micheal Brennan | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。受弱转向气流影响，气旋向西飘移，其组织结构起初变化甚微，但云层格局还是在8月22日改善，气象机构估计热带低气压于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}8月22日升级成热带风暴弗兰克<ref name="FrankTCR" />。虽然深层对流已经减弱，但气象部门经重新评估认为风暴当晚的持续风速为每小时95公里<ref name="Disc 5">{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Frank Discussion 5 | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183052/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.005.shtml? | author = Micheal Brennan | date = 2010-08-22 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。受强烈的东北向风切变影响，弗兰克在次日略有减弱<ref name="FrankTCR" />，到了8月24日清晨，美国国家飓风中心已经不再认为风暴会达到飓风标准<ref name="Disc 10">{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Frank Discussion 10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.010.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313014856/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.010.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | author = Daniel Brown | date = 2010-08-23 | archivedate = 2016-03-13 }}</ref>。虽然受到风切变影响，但气旋当晚依然出现深层对流爆发，组织结构也渐趋改善。{{lang|en|UTC}}上午8点34分和下午17点14分的微波图像表明风暴中有对流组成类似[[风眼|风眼]]的闭合环路，到8月25日清晨，弗兰克的风速已接近飓风下限。<ref name="FrankTCR" />

接下来的六小时里，风暴结构大幅改善，中心附近有非常强烈的大范围深层对流聚集，气象机构据此把弗兰克升级成飓风<ref name="Disc 16">{{cite report | author = Stacey Stewart | title = Hurricane Frank Discussion 16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313044404/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.016.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2010-08-25 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-13 }}</ref>。气旋还在逐渐强化，红外成像上的风眼时隐时现，微波图像上的风眼一直清晰可见。{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点，弗兰克在[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端以南约560公里海域达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]150公里，最低[[气压|气压]]978[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.88[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。此时的卫星图像显示风暴中心的风眼非常清晰，由中心密集云区层层环绕。<ref name="FrankTCR" />飓风朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]前进，于当晚开始减弱，风眼清晰度略有降低<ref name="Disc 22">{{cite report | author = Daniel Brown | title = Hurricane Frank Discussion 22 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | date = 2010-08-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.022.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313215225/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.022.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-13 }}</ref>。气旋继续减弱，结构渐趋混乱，风眼也随之坍塌<ref name="FrankTCR" />。8月27日，美国国家飓风中心把弗兰克降级成热带风暴，杂乱无章的对流在强烈风切变影响下位于中心以西，该机构因此预计风暴会在36小时内弱化成热带低气压<ref name="Disc 25">{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Frank Discussion 25 | archivedate = 2016-03-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324111303/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.025.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.025.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-13 | author = Robert Pasch | date = 2010-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。由于水温降低，气旋的所有雷暴活动急剧消散，风暴消退成云层漩涡，并在中层低压槽影响下转向北上<ref name="FrankTCR" /><ref name="Dsic 27">{{cite report | author = John Cangialosi | title = Tropical Storm Frank Discussion 27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.027.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-13 | date = 2010-08-28 | archivedate = 2016-03-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160320223326/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/ep09/ep092010.discus.027.shtml }}</ref>。8月28日清晨减弱成热带低气压后，弗兰克在下加利福尼亚州最南端的西南方向约370公里洋面退化成残留低气压区，最终于8月29日清晨消散<ref name="FrankTCR" />。

== 防灾措施、影响和善后 ==
[[File:Frank_aug_22_2010_1745Z.jpg|thumb]]

弗兰克自始至终没有登陆，但曾非常靠近墨西哥西部沿海地区，风暴发展期间，该国政府向部分沿海地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]。{{lang|en|UTC}}8月22日下午18点，气象机构发布热带风暴警告。8月24日气旋远离海岸后，上述预警和警告中止生效。<ref name="FrankTCR" />美国国家飓风中心指出，墨西哥地势较高的地区降雨量可能达到250毫米，引发危及生命的山洪和[[泥石流|泥石流]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Staff Writer | title = Danielle is a hurricane, Frank weakens | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | publisher = US. News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043454/http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2010/08/23/Danielle-is-hurricane-Frank-weakens/UPI-57401282566280/ | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2011-07-16 | date = 2010-08-27 | url = http://www.upi.com/Top_News/US/2010/08/23/Danielle-is-hurricane-Frank-weakens/UPI-57401282566280/ }}</ref>。经过评估，政府部门认为弗兰克很可能会对墨西哥太平洋沿岸地区构成重大破坏，也有较大可能重创南下加利福尼亚州<ref name="MXI">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Frank increases his power in the Mexican Pacific | archivedate = 2010-10-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101009093438/http://www.eluniversal.com/2010/08/26/int_ava_el-huracan-frank-inc_26A4388651.shtml | url = http://www.eluniversal.com/2010/08/26/int_ava_el-huracan-frank-inc_26A4388651.shtml | publisher = Eluniversal | accessdate = 2016-10-13 | date = 2010-08-26 }}</ref>。[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]、[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]和[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]都因可能出现倾盆大雨发布警报<ref name="MX 3">{{cite news | title = Hurricane moves toward Baja California Frank | accessdate = 2016-10-12 | deadurl = no | url = http://expansion.mx/nacional/2010/08/26/el-huracan-frank-avanza-hacia-baja-california | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160616160805/http://expansion.mx/nacional/2010/08/26/el-huracan-frank-avanza-hacia-baja-california | archivedate = 2016-06-16 | date = 2010-08-26 | publisher = Cable News Network }}</ref>。气象学家还称风暴可能影响[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]，其中以大浪的威胁为主<ref name="MX2">{{cite news | author1 = Leticia López | author2 = Dantiela Mendoza | title = Cierran puerto de Mazatlán ante cercanía de "Frank" | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161013054159/http://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones.php?id=612670 | url = http://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones.php?id=612670 | publisher = Editorial Noroeste, S.A. de C.V. | accessdate = 2011-06-18 | date = 2010-08-24 | archivedate = 2016-10-13 }}</ref>。

瓦哈卡州的米格尔·德拉马德里（{{lang|es|Miguel de la Madrid}}）24小时降雨量达360毫米，比其他地点都高。此外，另有多地在24小时内降下上百毫米雨量<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional | year = 2010 | title = Reseña del huracán “Frank” del Océano Pacífico | accessdate = 2016-10-13 | archivedate = 2016-10-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161013061705/http://smn.conagua.gob.mx/tools/DATA/Ciclones%20Tropicales/Ciclones/2010-Frank.pdf | url = http://smn.conagua.gob.mx/tools/DATA/Ciclones%20Tropicales/Ciclones/2010-Frank.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴还在墨西哥沿海地区产生强烈阵风<ref name="SW">{{cite web | last = Staff Writer | title = August major disasters roundup | url = http://www.continuitycentral.com/news05336.html | publisher = Community Central | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120716160110/http://continuitycentral.com/news05336.html | accessdate = 2012-07-16 | year = 2010 | archivedate = 2012-07-16 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，报导表明共有六人丧生。受洪灾影响，墨西哥有30套民房被毁，另外26套受损。[[山崩|山体滑坡]]致使两条主干线受损，另一条阻塞。多条河流泛滥成灾，<ref>{{cite news | author = IRZA | publisher = El Sol de Chilpancingo | date = 2010-08 | title = Estiman que "Frank" dejó daños por $14 millones}}</ref>导致七个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]中的171个农村社区被淹。[[塔巴斯科州|塔巴斯科州]]有超过80万人受灾，[[比亚埃尔莫萨|比亚埃尔莫萨]]爆发2007年后最严重的洪灾，约有8500人受灾。为避免局势恶化，当地居民把沙袋堆积起来阻挡洪水。<ref name="MXI" />瓦哈卡州有四人遇难，其中两人死于山体滑坡，182号联邦公路上有六辆车因山体滑坡冲下路面，又导致两人丧生<ref name="CNN WS">{{cite news |title=Hurricane Frank leaves death, destruction behind as it moves off shore |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100929010308/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/americas/08/25/hurricane.frank/index.html |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/americas/08/25/hurricane.frank/index.html |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2011-07-16 |author=CNN wire staff |date=2010-08-26 |archivedate=2010-09-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。共有六万人无家可归，暴雨导致许多桥梁和道路被毁，许多社区同外界的交通中断<ref name="MX 3"/>。

风暴过去后，[[墨西哥陆军|墨西哥陆军]]向灾民提供协助<ref name="MXI" />。共有110个社区请求政府援助。截至9月14日，送抵灾区派发的食品包裹估计已有20万个。修复飓风弗兰克造成破坏的成本共计为一亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（2010年墨西哥比索，相当于同年的830万美元）。<ref>{{cite news | author = Sandra Pacheco | publisher = CNX Oaxaca | date = 2010-09-14 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | title = Necesarios más de 100 mdp para atender emergencia: URO | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714151304/http://cnxoaxaca.com/?mod=noticias&i=6930&is=5 | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | url = http://cnxoaxaca.com/?mod=noticias&i=6930&is=5 }}</ref>

